<section id="about" class="about section">
  <div class="container aos-init aos-animate" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
    <div class="row align-items-xl-center gy-5">
      <div class="col-xl-7 content">
        <h2>Furniture Group of India</h2>
        <p>Furniture Group of India is one of the country’s leading names in quality furniture design, manufacturing, and distribution. Founded with a passion for craftsmanship and innovation, we bring together traditional artistry and modern technology to create furniture that enhances every space — from homes and offices to hotels and institutions.<br>
<br>
With a commitment to excellence, we take pride in producing furniture that combines elegance, comfort, and durability. Our collections are crafted using premium materials and sustainable practices, reflecting our dedication to both quality and environmental responsibility.<br>
<br>
At Furniture Group of India, we believe furniture is more than just décor — it’s a statement of lifestyle and identity. Our expert designers and craftsmen work tirelessly to deliver products that are functional, stylish, and built to last.<br>
<br>
Today, we serve customers across India through our extensive network of showrooms, dealers, and online platforms, continuing to redefine the standards of furniture design and manufacturing in the country.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xl-5">
        <div class="row gy-4 icon-boxes">
          <div class="abt-thumb2">
            <img src="./hero_files/1760001944.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="About Us Image">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
